  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Lebanon - ICRC-LRC cash and livelihoods programme</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The British Red Cross (BRC) in collaboration with the ICRC and Lebanese Red Cross (LRC) seeks to address the needs and vulnerabilities of the population in Arsal Lebanon as well as continue and strengthen the Movement response to the Syria Crisis through this partnership project. In the long-term this project has the potential and scalability to be replicated in vulnerable communities across Lebanon Syria and neighbouring countries as appropriate and as funding permits.</narrative>
  </description>
